    "content": "#  API\n\n API \n\n## \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `id` | string |  |\n| `name` | string |  |\n| `type` | string | PERSONORGANIZATIONLOCATION  |\n| `description` | string |  |\n| `metadata` | object |  |\n| `createdAt` | string | ISO 8601  |\n| `updatedAt` | string | ISO 8601  |\n\n## \n\n|  |  |\n|------|------|\n| `PERSON` |  |\n| `ORGANIZATION` |  |\n| `LOCATION` |  |\n| `PRODUCT` |  |\n| `EVENT` |  |\n| `CONCEPT` |  |\n| `OTHER` |  |\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nPOST /v1/entities\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `name` | string |  |  |\n| `type` | string |  |  |\n| `description` | string |  |  |\n| `metadata` | object |  |  |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/entities \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"name\": \"\",\n    \"type\": \"PERSON\",\n    \"description\": \"TypeScript \",\n    \"metadata\": {\n      \"department\": \"\",\n      \"role\": \"\"\n    }\n  }'\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"ent_abc123\",\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"type\": \"PERSON\",\n  \"description\": \"TypeScript \",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"department\": \"\",\n    \"role\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nGET /v1/entities\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `type` | string |  |  |\n| `search` | string |  |  |\n| `page` | number |  | 1 |\n| `limit` | number |  | 20100 |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET \"https://api.memokit.dev/v1/entities?type=PERSON&limit=10\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ent_abc123\",\n      \"name\": \"\",\n      \"type\": \"PERSON\",\n      \"description\": \"TypeScript \",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n      \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ent_def456\",\n      \"name\": \"\",\n      \"type\": \"PERSON\",\n      \"description\": \"\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-14T09:00:00Z\",\n      \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-14T09:00:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"total\": 25,\n    \"totalPages\": 3\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n ID \n\n```\nGET /v1/entities/:id\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `id` | string |  ID |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET https://api.memokit.dev/v1/entities/ent_abc123 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"ent_abc123\",\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"type\": \"PERSON\",\n  \"description\": \"TypeScript \",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"department\": \"\",\n    \"role\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nDELETE /v1/entities/:id\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `id` | string |  ID |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X DELETE https://api.memokit.dev/v1/entities/ent_abc123 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"id\": \"ent_abc123\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n|  |  |\n|--------|------|\n| `ENTITY_NOT_FOUND` |  |\n| `INVALID_ENTITY_TYPE` |  |\n| `NAME_REQUIRED` |  |",
