    "content": "# API \n\n Memokit  API  RESTful  JSON \n\n##  URL\n\n```\nhttps://api.memokit.dev\n```\n\n## \n\n Authorization  API \n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\n```\n\n [](/zh/docs/getting-started/authentication)\n\n## API \n\n API  **v1** `/v1/` \n\n## \n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `/v1/memories` |  |\n| `POST` | `/v1/memories/search` |  |\n| `GET` | `/v1/memories` |  |\n| `GET` | `/v1/memories/:id` |  |\n| `DELETE` | `/v1/memories/:id` |  |\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `/v1/entities` |  |\n| `GET` | `/v1/entities` |  |\n| `DELETE` | `/v1/entities/:id` |  |\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `/v1/relations` |  |\n| `GET` | `/v1/relations` |  |\n| `DELETE` | `/v1/relations/:id` |  |\n\n## \n\n|  |  |\n|--------|------|\n| `200` |  |\n| `201` |  |\n| `400` |  -  |\n| `401` |  - API  |\n| `403` |  -  |\n| `404` |  |\n| `429` |  -  |\n| `500` |  |\n\n## \n\n\n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"ERROR_CODE\",\n    \"message\": \"\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## \n\n\n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `page` | number | 1 |  |\n| `limit` | number | 20 |  100 |\n\n\n\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [...],\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"limit\": 20,\n    \"total\": 150,\n    \"totalPages\": 8\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## \n\n [](/zh/docs/guides/rate-limits)",
