    "content": "#  API\n\n API \n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nPOST /v1/memories\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `content` | string |  |  10,000  |\n| `userId` | string |  |  |\n| `agentId` | string |  |  |\n| `tags` | string[] |  |  |\n| `metadata` | object |  |  |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"content\": \" Python \",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"agentId\": \"agent_456\",\n    \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n    \"metadata\": {\n      \"source\": \"chat\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"sess_789\"\n    }\n  }'\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"mem_abc123def456\",\n  \"content\": \" Python \",\n  \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n  \"agentId\": \"agent_456\",\n  \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"source\": \"chat\",\n    \"sessionId\": \"sess_789\"\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nPOST /v1/memories/search\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `query` | string |  |  |\n| `userId` | string |  |  ID  |\n| `agentId` | string |  |  ID  |\n| `tags` | string[] |  | AND  |\n| `limit` | number |  | 10100 |\n| `threshold` | number |  | 0-10.5 |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories/search \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"query\": \"\",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"limit\": 5,\n    \"threshold\": 0.6\n  }'\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mem_abc123def456\",\n      \"content\": \" Python \",\n      \"score\": 0.87,\n      \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n      \"agentId\": \"agent_456\",\n      \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mem_xyz789\",\n      \"content\": \" JavaScript  Web \",\n      \"score\": 0.74,\n      \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n      \"tags\": [\"\"],\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-14T15:20:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n`score` 0-1\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nGET /v1/memories\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|------|\n| `userId` | string |  |  ID  |\n| `agentId` | string |  |  ID  |\n| `tags` | string |  |  |\n| `page` | number |  | 1 |\n| `limit` | number |  | 20100 |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET \"https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories?userId=user_123&limit=10\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mem_abc123def456\",\n      \"content\": \" Python \",\n      \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n      \"agentId\": \"agent_456\",\n      \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n      \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"pagination\": {\n    \"page\": 1,\n    \"limit\": 10,\n    \"total\": 45,\n    \"totalPages\": 5\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n ID \n\n```\nGET /v1/memories/:id\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `id` | string |  ID |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories/mem_abc123def456 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"mem_abc123def456\",\n  \"content\": \" Python \",\n  \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n  \"agentId\": \"agent_456\",\n  \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"source\": \"chat\",\n    \"sessionId\": \"sess_789\"\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"updatedAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n\n\n```\nDELETE /v1/memories/:id\n```\n\n### \n\n|  |  |  |\n|------|------|------|\n| `id` | string |  ID |\n\n### \n\n```bash\ncurl -X DELETE https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories/mem_abc123def456 \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"id\": \"mem_abc123def456\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## \n\n|  |  |\n|--------|------|\n| `MEMORY_NOT_FOUND` |  |\n| `CONTENT_TOO_LONG` |  10,000  |\n| `INVALID_USER_ID` |  ID |\n| `QUOTA_EXCEEDED` |  |",
