    "content": "# Webhooks\n\nWebhooks  Memokit  HTTP \n\n## \n\n webhook Memokit  URL  HTTP POST  API \n\n## Webhook \n\n|  |  |\n|------|------|\n| `memory.created` |  |\n| `memory.updated` |  |\n| `memory.deleted` |  |\n\n## Webhook \n\n webhook \n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"wh_delivery_abc123\",\n  \"event\": \"memory.created\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"mem_abc123\",\n    \"content\": \"...\",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n##  Webhooks\n\n### 1.  Webhook \n\n POST \n\n```javascript\n// Express.js \napp.post('/webhooks/memokit', (req, res) => {\n  const signature = req.headers['x-memokit-signature'];\n  const payload = req.body;\n\n  // \n  if (!verifySignature(payload, signature, webhookSecret)) {\n    return res.status(401).send('');\n  }\n\n  // \n  switch (payload.event) {\n    case 'memory.created':\n      handleMemoryCreated(payload.data);\n      break;\n    case 'memory.updated':\n      handleMemoryUpdated(payload.data);\n      break;\n    case 'memory.deleted':\n      handleMemoryDeleted(payload.data);\n      break;\n  }\n\n  res.status(200).send('OK');\n});\n```\n\n### 2.  Webhook\n\n Memokit \n\n1.  **Webhooks**\n2.  ** Webhook**\n3.  URL\n4. \n5.  webhook\n\n### 3. \n\n webhook \n\n```\nX-Memokit-Signature: sha256=abc123...\n```\n\n HMAC-SHA256 \n\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nfunction verifySignature(payload, signature, secret) {\n  const expectedSignature = 'sha256=' + crypto\n    .createHmac('sha256', secret)\n    .update(JSON.stringify(payload))\n    .digest('hex');\n\n  return crypto.timingSafeEqual(\n    Buffer.from(signature),\n    Buffer.from(expectedSignature)\n  );\n}\n```\n\n## Webhook \n\n 2xx Memokit \n\n|  |  |\n|---------|------|\n| 1 |  |\n| 2 | 1  |\n| 3 | 5  |\n| 4 | 30  |\n| 5 | 2  |\n\n5 webhook \n\n## \n\n### \n\n 200  webhook \n\n```javascript\napp.post('/webhooks/memokit', async (req, res) => {\n  // \n  if (!verifySignature(req.body, req.headers['x-memokit-signature'], secret)) {\n    return res.status(401).send('');\n  }\n\n  // \n  await queue.add('process-webhook', req.body);\n\n  // \n  res.status(200).send('OK');\n});\n```\n\n### \n\nWebhook  ID \n\n```javascript\nasync function processWebhook(payload) {\n  const deliveryId = payload.id;\n\n  // \n  if (await isDeliveryProcessed(deliveryId)) {\n    return;\n  }\n\n  //  webhook\n  await handleWebhookEvent(payload);\n\n  // \n  await markDeliveryProcessed(deliveryId);\n}\n```\n\n###  HTTPS\n\n HTTPS  webhook \n\n##  Webhook \n\n Memokit  webhook \n\n1.  **Webhooks**\n2.  webhook\n3.  **** \n\n\n\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- /\n\n## \n\n|  |  |\n|--------|------|\n| `WEBHOOK_NOT_FOUND` |  webhook  |\n| `INVALID_WEBHOOK_URL` | webhook URL  |\n| `WEBHOOK_DELIVERY_FAILED` |  webhook  |",
