    "content": "# \n\n Memokit API  API \n\n## API \n\nAPI  Memokit API  API \n\n-  `mk_` \n- \n- \n- \n\n##  API \n\n1.  [Memokit ](https://console.memokit.dev)\n2.  **API **\n3.  ** API **\n4. \n5. \n\n> **** API \n\n##  API \n\n `Authorization`  API \n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n### \n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\n```\n\n## \n\n### \n\n-  API \n- \n- \n\n```bash\n# \nexport MEMOKIT_API_KEY=\"mk_your_api_key\"\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer $MEMOKIT_API_KEY\" ...\n```\n\n### \n\n- \n- \n- \n\n### \n\n- \n- \n\n##  API \n\n### \n\n **API ** \n\n- \n- \n- \n- /\n\n### \n\n\n\n1.  **API **\n2. \n3.  **** \n4. \n\n\n\n## \n\n###  Authorization \n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\",\n    \"message\": \" Authorization \"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n###  API \n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"INVALID_API_KEY\",\n    \"message\": \" API \"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n###  API \n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"API_KEY_REVOKED\",\n    \"message\": \" API \"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## \n\n- [](/zh/docs/getting-started/quickstart) -  API \n- [](/zh/docs/guides/rate-limits) - \n- [API ](/zh/docs/api-reference) - ",
