    "content": "# \n\n Memokit API \n\n##  1  API \n\n1.  [console.memokit.dev](https://console.memokit.dev) \n2.  **API **\n3.  ** API **\n4.  API  `mk_` \n\n> **** API \n\n##  2 \n\n curl \n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"content\": \" TypeScript  React\",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"]\n  }'\n```\n\n\n\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": \"mem_abc123\",\n  \"content\": \" TypeScript  React\",\n  \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n  \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n  \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n##  3 \n\n\n\n```bash\n# \ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"content\": \" VS Code  IDE\",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"tags\": [\"\"]\n  }'\n\n# \ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"content\": \" Next.js \",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"]\n  }'\n```\n\n##  4 \n\n\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories/search \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"query\": \"\",\n    \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n    \"limit\": 5\n  }'\n```\n\n\n\n```json\n{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mem_abc123\",\n      \"content\": \" TypeScript  React\",\n      \"score\": 0.89,\n      \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n      \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mem_def456\",\n      \"content\": \" Next.js \",\n      \"score\": 0.72,\n      \"userId\": \"user_123\",\n      \"tags\": [\"\", \"\"],\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-01-15T10:32:00Z\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n\n\n##  5 \n\n\n\n```bash\ncurl -X GET \"https://api.memokit.dev/v1/memories?userId=user_123&limit=10\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer mk_your_api_key\"\n```\n\n## \n\n\n\n- [](/zh/docs/getting-started/authentication) -  API \n- [ API](/zh/docs/api-reference/memories) -  API \n- [](/zh/docs/api-reference/entities) - \n- [Webhooks](/zh/docs/api-reference/webhooks) - ",
